%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%

sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (React)
    participant TQ as TanStack Query
    participant EF as Edge Function
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant AI as AI Service

    Note over U,AI: Standard Data Fetch Pattern
    U->>FE: Navigate to page
    FE->>TQ: useQuery hook called
    TQ->>EF: POST /functions/v1/{function}
    EF->>DB: Query data
    DB-->>EF: Return rows
    EF-->>TQ: JSON response
    TQ-->>FE: Cached data
    FE-->>U: Render UI

    Note over U,AI: AI Content Generation (Batch)
    U->>FE: Request slide generation
    FE->>EF: POST /submit-batch-slides
    EF->>AI: Submit to Vertex AI Batch
    AI-->>EF: Batch job ID
    EF->>DB: Create batch_jobs record
    EF-->>FE: Return job ID

    loop Poll every 30s
        FE->>EF: POST /poll-batch-status
        EF->>AI: Check batch status
        AI-->>EF: Processing / Complete
        EF-->>FE: Status update
    end

    AI-->>EF: Batch complete callback
    EF->>DB: Update teaching_units
    FE->>TQ: Invalidate queries
    TQ->>EF: Refetch data
    FE-->>U: Show generated content

    Note over U,AI: Authentication Flow
    U->>FE: Login with email/password
    FE->>EF: Supabase Auth
    EF-->>FE: JWT token
    FE->>FE: Store in localStorage
    U->>FE: Access protected page
    FE->>EF: Request with JWT
    EF->>EF: Validate JWT
    EF->>DB: Query with user context
    DB-->>EF: RLS-filtered data
    EF-->>FE: Authorized response
